data.description: Full Sized Quad In Lynwood!!! This lovingly cared for home has room for everyone in its 4 levels. It's cedar and brick exterior give it nice curb appeal while the large corner lot, fenced yard, and back patio allow for outdoor enjoyment. The main floor has a spacious Kitchen with room for a table plus formal Dining and Living rooms. Up on the 2nd level the bedrooms all have beautiful hardwood floors and there's a modern bath. The Lower Level has a wonderful Family Room and another full bath. There is a fireplace and bar as well. The basement provides a finished Rec Room plus laundry and storage. The roof was replaced last year. This long term owner has cherished memories raising their family in this house, and an out of state move provides the opportunity for you to start building your cherished memories here. Make your appointment to come and see all this wonderful house has to offer today!
